channel.description:
Welcome to BananaNation Minecraft Server. On our server we have friendly players and staff that will answer all your questions. We have many cool things for you to enjoy on our server. We have Team Fortress 2, Skyblock. Spleef, and to come Survival Games. In addition to the survival part of the game we have added guns to make your experience fun. We have everything on our server which makes me proud but there is one thing missing. PLAYERS!. So please join the server and HAVE FUN :D
